storyInfo: Infected creatures and strange mercenaries attack the Infected community of Long Spring. Team Rainbow leaps into the fray to help them avert disaster, but the situation takes an unexpected turn for the worse.

attributes.content: Cease fire! Watch out for civilians!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: They're getting away, Cohen!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Don't bother with them, protect the others!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Someone come here, there are injured people here.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Let's bring them inside.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Doctor! Are you ok?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'm here! I'm fine!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: My leg! My leg is broken! My leg! ......
attributes.name: Infected Townsfolk

attributes.content: Calm down, your leg is still here, it's just dislocated. Grit your teeth.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Mama... Mamaaa...
attributes.name: Infected Girl

attributes.content: Has anyone seen Algar's mother?
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Help me......please......
attributes.name: Wounded Townsfolk

attributes.content: We're running out of bandages......
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Those... (profanity)!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Is there a fire over there?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Isn't the town center in that direction?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Looks like this isn't the only place that was attacked.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Why? Where did the lord's guards go?
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Don't care about those guards or whatever anymore.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: There are sounds of fighting everywhere now, and it's only getting worse. We can't stay here, it's too wide open.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Let's move those wounded behind this building for now!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Monsters! The monsters have come again!
attributes.name: Infected Townsfolk

attributes.content: Help!
attributes.name: Infected Woman

attributes.content: This is endless!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Alexsandr! Get on the roof and cover us!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: There's no time, doctor. We need to leave this place.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: But, where can we go?
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Let's go to your clinic.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: These Infected......
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Don't worry too much about it, let's get everyone to go to your clinic first.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: ......Alright.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Someone lend a hand! He can't walk anymore!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Kötz, can you go and check if there's anyone else hiding in these houses? Let's get everyone here to the clinic.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Stay safe!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: ......This is really a disaster.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Forty plus people......Is everyone here?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Everyone we've rescued......is here.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: How many are we missing?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Quite a number, maybe they went to the other side of the town.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: But some old ones......they didn't make it......
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Don't beat yourself up, it's not your fault.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: These monsters, where are they from? Are they trained beasts?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I don't know......I've never seen anything like them before.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: When those thugs drew their weapons, these monsters began burrowing out of the ground.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Who cares where they came from. How can there be so many of them?!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: How's the surrounding situation?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: A big mess.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: There's sounds of combat from the other side of the town. I don't know what happened there.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: How much ammo do we have left?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Not much, I only have four magazines left. If Alexsandr runs out of ammo then we're in big trouble.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Ammo isn't the biggest problem right now. This house isn't going to last much longer.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Judging by those monsters' size, if we let even one or two escape, they will definitely smash through this wall and it'll be impossible to stop them then. We need a plan.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Doctor, how are the patients doing?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Many of them are wounded, I'm only able to do some simple treatment.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: We're lacking bandages and disinfectants.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Is there any way to leave the town for now?
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Where would we go after leaving town? While bringing so many with us?
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Without food and water, going onto the wasteland means certain death.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I don't think these monsters will give up on attacking us. If we get to the wastelands, we'll just be in a worse position without any cover or means of hiding ourselves. Besides, we've all witnessed their burrowing abilities......
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I know a place......It might be safe.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: There's a special building at the south side of town. It might be the safest place in town, barring the lord's residence.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Do elaborate.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: There was this medical organization called Rhodes Island which rented a piece of land at the edge of town.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Later they hired workers to dig a fair amount of soil and stone and built a very solid house there.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: ......It could be the strongest building around here? It looks just like a fortress.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: How do you know that this 'Rhodes Island' would be willing to help us?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: There's only one watchman at that building, and I know him. I've purchased some medical supplies from him before.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: There's a lot of soil, most likely they dug out a basement.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Sounds like a safe house used by mercenaries.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Doesn't sound reliable.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Unless we have a better option, I suggest we take a look.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Without food nor water, staying in this place is no different than waiting for death.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: That building is at the edge of town. We can head over from outside town to avoid being seen by others.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Kötz, is your shield still usable?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Half of it. I can use it to bash someone......probably.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I need someone to go with me, to help protect the doctor.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'll go. Worse comes to worst I can always shield the doctor with my body.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Don't talk crap.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Kötz and I will go with the doctor to check out that 'safe house.' Tina, you stay here with Alexsandr.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Doctor, no matter what happens next, please follow my orders.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Kötz, protect the doctor well.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'll keep him safe.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I don't see any lights, is there no one there?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Keep your distance. This building's door has been smashed.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Even here......
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: What are these thugs' goals? To rob and plunder like common bandits?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Help! Anyone! Help me!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: I......I don't want to die......Damn it......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: It's the watchman!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Don't move and stay here.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'll go have a look.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: ......If only I didn't take this job......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: I don't want to die here......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Who are you!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Don't move, your leg's broken.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: M......mercenaries......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Don't kill me! I beg you! Don't kill me! I really don't know where the key is! I'm just a simple watchman!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Please believe me! I really don't know!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Calm down! I'm here to help.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: You......you're not together with those guys......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Help me! Help me!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: I! Said! Calm down!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Kötz! Bring the doctor!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Mister Occphen, your leg......
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: You......you're that Infected doctor!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Oh, thank heavens!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Don't worry, let me look at your leg.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Man, this place has been turned upside down.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: The inside looks a lot smaller than the outside.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Secret doors, hidden rooms and fortified walls. Aren't all safe houses like that?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: What's this?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Radio equipment? It's completely destroyed though.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Such a large machine, looks very retro. Turns out this world also had communications equipment like this.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: They even have cars after all, it's not strange for them to have radio.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: There were other 'broken electronics' back at the run-down house we stayed at before, like the fridge, fans, a kettle......Though none of them actually used electricity.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Just like this wireless radio, and that car we got.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: All these machines have a device filled with black crystals. I suppose that is the energy source for these devices.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Ouch ouch ouch! Please be gentler, doctor!
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Please bear with it!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: ......Luckily it's not very serious, the bone isn't broken.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: You're the person in charge of this place?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: This is......Rhodes Island's branch office. I'm actually just a simple watchman.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Let me guess, those thugs came here and forced you to open the basement door, but you persisted in your duty and kept playing dumb, which resulted in you getting beaten up and left here to die?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: ......Something like that.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Wait, how did you know there's a basement?
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: You've been tricked. We're actually the thugs' backup, here to get you to confess everything.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: What? ?
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Kötz!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Don't get angry, I'm just trying to liven up the atmosphere.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: You......What are you actually planning to do?
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Don't worry, they're good people. They've been protecting the inhabitants of the infected zone all this while.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: The infected zone was attacked as well? ?
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: This......It's messed up.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: What about the lord's soldiers? Where are Lord Tulla's soldiers?
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: The lord's soldiers still haven't appeared. They might be in trouble as well.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Mister Watchman, we need your help.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: But, what can I do to help? I can't even stand up right now.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: The Infected townsfolk have also been attacked, with many of them being injured and the buildings of the infected zone suffering heavy damages.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: We need you to open up the safe house and let them hide in here.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: That...
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: In return, we will guarantee your safety. You can trust us.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: But, but I...
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Based on the contract I signed with Rhodes Island, the entire safe house is the property of Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: ......I don't have the authority......
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Alright, let them come. Losing my job is better than losing my life.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: Thank you!
attributes.name: Miarow
